DNSSEC Roadblock Avoidance
2016", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="This document describes problems that a Validating DNS resolver, stub-resolver, or application might run into within a non-compliant infrastructure.  It outlines potential detection and mitigation techniques.  The scope of the document is to create a shared approach to detect and overcome network issues that a DNSSEC software/system may face.", style=filled, fillcolor=green]; 

